    "name": "Smart Task & Team Management Portal",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the Smart Task & Team Management Portal.\n\n## Setup\n1. Import this collection into Postman\n2. The `{{baseUrl}}` variable is pre-set to `http://localhost:5000/api`\n3. Run the **Login** or **Register** request first — the token will be automatically saved\n4. All authenticated requests will use the saved `{{token}}` automatically\n\n## Authentication\nThe collection uses Bearer Token authentication. After logging in, a test script automatically extracts the token from the response and stores it in the `{{token}}` collection variable.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "baseUrl",
      "value": "http://localhost:5000/api",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "token",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "userId",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "projectId",
